<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>派訓名單轉換工具 V4.2 - 表頭同步與嚴格排序版</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.18.5/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jspdf/2.5.1/jspdf.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --bg:#fff;--bg2:#f5f5f4;--bg3:#eeede9;
  --border:rgba(0,0,0,.10);--border2:rgba(0,0,0,.18);
  --text:#1a1a18;--text2:#6b6b67;--text3:#9b9b97;
  --blue:#185FA5;--blue-bg:#E6F1FB;
  --green:#3B6D11;--green-bg:#EAF3DE;--green-bd:#C0DD97;
  --red:#A32D2D;--r:10px;--rs:6px
}
body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI','PingFang TC','Microsoft JhengHei',sans-serif;background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;padding:2rem 1rem}
.wrap{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto}
h1{font-size:20px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.25rem}
.sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:2rem}
.steps{display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:.75rem}
.sdot{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;flex-shrink:0;border:1.5px solid var(--border2);background:var(--bg2);color:var(--text2)}
.sdot.active{background:var(--blue);color:#fff;border-color:var(--blue)}
.sdot.done{background:var(--green);color:#fff;border-color:var(--green)}
.sline{flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border)}
.sline.done{background:var(--green)}
.slabels{display:flex;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
.slabel{flex:1;font-size:11px;color:var(--text3)}
.slabel.active{color:var(--blue);font-weight:600}.slabel.done{color:var(--green)}
.panel{background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);padding:1.25rem;margin-bottom:1rem;box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.04)}
.ptitle{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:.5rem}
.dstatus{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:var(--rs);border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:.75rem;font-size:13px;background:var(--bg2)}
.dstatus.ok{background:var(--green-bg);border-color:var(--green-bd)}
.dropzone{display:block;width:100%;border:1.5px dashed var(--border2);border-radius:var(--rs);padding:1.5rem;text-align:center;cursor:pointer;background:var(--bg2);position:relative}
.dropzone input[type=file]{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;opacity:0;cursor:pointer}
.flist{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--rs);overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:.75rem}
.frow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:9px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-size:13px;background:var(--bg)}
.brow{display:flex;gap:8px;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:1.25rem}
.btn{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;padding:8px 18px;border-radius:var(--rs);cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--border2);background:var(--bg);font-family:inherit}
.btn.p{background:var(--blue);color:#fff;border-color:var(--blue)}
.log{background:#1e1e1e;border-radius:var(--rs);padding:12px 14px;font-size:12px;font-family:'SF Mono',monospace;color:#ccc;max-height:180px;overflow-y:auto;line-height:1.8}
.log .ok{color:#7ec870}.log .info{color:#79b8ff}
.sgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:10px;margin-bottom:1rem}
.scard{background:var(--bg2);border-radius:var(--rs);padding:.85rem .5rem;text-align:center}
.snum{font-size:22px;font-weight:700}.slbl2{font-size:10px;color:var(--text2);margin-top:3px}
.dl-item{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.dl-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:600}
.hidden{display:none!important}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <h1>📋 派訓名單轉換工具 V4.2</h1>
  <p class="sub">依課程資訊動態更新表頭內容，並嚴格執行工號排序</p>

  <div class="steps">
    <div class="sdot active" id="dot1">1</div><div class="sline" id="line1"></div>
    <div class="sdot" id="dot2">2</div><div class="sline" id="line2"></div>
    <div class="sdot" id="dot3">3</div><div class="sline" id="line3"></div>
    <div class="sdot" id="dot4">4</div>
  </div>
  <div class="slabels">
    <span class="slabel active" id="lbl1">人事資料</span>
    <span class="slabel" id="lbl2">課程資訊</span>
    <span class="slabel" id="lbl3">派訓名單</span>
    <span class="slabel" id="lbl4">產出結果</span>
  </div>

  <div id="step1">
    <div class="panel">
      <div class="ptitle">步驟 1：人事總表 (對應部門)</div>
      <div class="dstatus" id="s1status">未載入</div>
      <label class="dropzone">
